have applied pursuant to section 4(c)(8) of the Bank Holding Company Act (12 U.S.C. 1843(c)(8)) (BHC Act) and  225.23(a)
of the Board's Regulation Y (12 CFR 225.23(a)) to engage through InfiNet Payment Services, Inc., Hackensack, New
