m. Other information as listed in product package insert.


4.  The firm will provide a copy of U.S. Pharmacopeia Official Monograph (article), if appropriate.

5.  The firm's authorized responsible representative will sign and submit a statement that the firm is in compliance
with FDA's Current Good Manufacturing Practice (GMP) regulations. 

6.  The firm will provide a copy of the most recent FD-483, FDA Notice of Inspectional Observations that
